{"tid":1665531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721=死穴] 西鐵綫元朗站明日下午2時起臨時關閉","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T23:59:15.000Z","uid":231583,"like":215,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6190af64318a77bba93fbbe3ef8c29ea5e7dd4","tid":1665531,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵：西鐵綫元朗站明日下午2時起臨時關閉<br />\n<br />\n除機場快綫外，港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士今天的服務時間已經完結。港鐵表示，經審視復修工作的進度，並與相關政府部門進行風險評估後，明天除機場快綫外的港鐵各綫、輕鐵及港鐵巴士服務將提早於晚上10時結束。另外，西鐵綫元朗站會於下午2時起臨時關閉，乘客請預早計劃行程及考慮使用其他交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-20 23:05:56 RTHK TG<br />\n<br />\n係咪好驚人靜坐呀黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />721完全係民意100%企係我地呢到既轉捩點"},{"pid":"3655557009aebe14431f94f4957493a677178667","tid":1665531,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"雖然出面仲未完，但都想大家幫幫手推定聽日大西北行動POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9e431a1d19698b4de28fff73511462df12172b","tid":1665531,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"勞煩各位幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e74718d584ed912c2317290bbacd075df223ae4","tid":1665531,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f127632fecf3a94ed36b8b61416f87dfb043fd","tid":1665531,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"勁推"},{"pid":"4e6acae3426e528064da6b9d401fe36c5ea1a248","tid":1665531,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f